  "texts": [
    "Establishing unified guidelines, standardized experimental protocols, and common evaluation criteria is crucial for enhancing reproducibility and fostering consensus in the sensory AI research community.",
    "Moreover, multimodal integration presents another critical gap.",
    "Flavor perception naturally involves interactions between olfactory, gustatory, visual, and even auditory sensory inputs.",
    "Yet, most existing AI models treat these sensory modalities in isolation, failing to capture their complex, synergistic relationships.",
    "Developing robust multimodal frameworks that effectively integrate and analyze data from multiple sensory channels simultaneously is necessary for realistically modeling human sensory experiences."
  ],
